{"types":[{"section":"\n{{fr-verb}}\n\n# {{lb|fr|informal|figuratively}} to [[lose one's bearings]], to be [[all]] [[at sea]]\n#: {{syn|fr|perdre la boussole}}\n\n====Usage notes====\nChiefly used in negative sentences: {{m|fr||ne pas perdre le nord|not to lose sight of one's goals, not to miss an occasion to progress towards one's goals}}. Especially said of people who don't lose sight of their interests in financial matters, and are attentive with money.\n\n====See also====\n* {{l|fr|garder le sens des réalités}}\n* {{l|fr|avoir de la suite dans les idées}}\n\n{{cln|fr|negative polarity items}}","alt":[],"syn":["perdre la boussole"],"type":"verb","forms":[{"mod":"inf","aux":["avoir"],"pronom":false}],"html":"<p><span class=\"headword-line\"><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/perdre#French\" title=\"perdre\">perdre</a> <a href=\"/wiki/le#French\" title=\"le\">le</a> <a href=\"/wiki/nord#French\" title=\"nord\">nord</a></strong></span>\n</p><ol><li><span class=\"usage-label-sense\"><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content label-content\"><a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#informal\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">informal</a><span class=\"ib-comma label-comma\">,</span> <a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#figurative\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">figuratively</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">)</span></span> to <a href=\"/wiki/lose_one%27s_bearings\" title=\"lose one's bearings\">lose one's bearings</a>, to be <a href=\"/wiki/all\" title=\"all\">all</a> <a href=\"/wiki/at_sea\" title=\"at sea\">at sea</a>\n<dl><dd><span class=\"nyms synonym\"><span class=\"defdate\">Synonym:</span> <span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/perdre_la_boussole#French\" title=\"perdre la boussole\">perdre la boussole</a></span></span></dd></dl></li></ol><div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading4\"><h4 id=\"Usage_notes\">Usage notes</h4><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=perdre_le_nord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Usage notes\"><span>edit</span></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></div><p>Chiefly used in negative sentences: <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"fr\">ne pas perdre le nord</i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">“</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">not to lose sight of one's goals, not to miss an occasion to progress towards one's goals</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">”</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span>. Especially said of people who don't lose sight of their interests in financial matters, and are attentive with money.\n</p><div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading4\"><h4 id=\"See_also\">See also</h4><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=perdre_le_nord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span>edit</span></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></div><ul><li><span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/garder_le_sens_des_r%C3%A9alit%C3%A9s#French\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"garder le sens des réalités\">garder le sens des réalités</a></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/avoir_de_la_suite_dans_les_id%C3%A9es#French\" title=\"avoir de la suite dans les idées\">avoir de la suite dans les idées</a></span></li></ul>","trans":["to lose one's bearings, to be all at sea"]}],"title":"perdre le nord","id":"7042640","audios":[{"name":"LL-Q150 (fra)-Lyokoï-perdre le nord.wav","url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d6/LL-Q150_%28fra%29-Lyoko%C3%AF-perdre_le_nord.wav"}],"ipas":["/pɛʁ.dʁə l(ə) nɔʁ/"],"pronunSection":"\n* {{fr-IPA}}\n* {{audio|fr|LL-Q150 (fra)-Lyokoï-perdre le nord.wav}}\n\n","pronunHtml":"<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:International_Phonetic_Alphabet\" title=\"Wiktionary:Internatio